Lab 1 : Option pricing using the Binomial model.
Lab 2 : Sensitivity analysis of European option prices.
Lab 3 : American and Lookback options.
Lab 4 : Compute the Markowitz efficient frontier and the Capital Market Line.
Lab 5 : Plot the Markowitz efficient frontier.
Lab 6 : Plot returns from market indices, namely Sensex and Nifty.
Lab 7 : European option pricing in the classical BSM framework and its sensitivity analysis.
Lab 8 : Option pricing using historical market data.
Lab 9 : Analyse historical option price market data. (incomplete)
Lab 10: Simulate asset price by Geometric Brownian motion and use it to price Asian options.
Lab 11: Plot term structure yield on the basis of interest rate models. (incomplete)
